             was indicted for <rs id="t18200628-11-off52" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200628-11-off52" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18200628-11-off52" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18200628-11-cd53" type="crimeDate">7th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200628-11-off52 t18200628-11-cd53"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18200628-11-off54 t18200628-11-cd53"></join>, 18 lbs. of sugar, value 16 s.; 10 lbs. of currants, value 9 s., and 3 lbs. of other sugar, value 1 s. 6 d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18200628-11-victim151" type="victimName">
                     Nathaniel 
                     Fenn
                  <interp inst="t18200628-11-victim151" type="surname" value="Fenn"></interp>
