               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SMALL - <rs id="t18200628-11-verdict60" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18200628-11-verdict60" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 25.</p>
